replies.bodyText:
Okay, my suggested solution doesn't work, and it seems that the only way to avoid rawtypes warnings is to do the following:
final Class<?> clazz = field.getType();
final Enum<?> enumValue = Enum.valueOf(clazz.asSubclass(Enum.class), valueAsString);

Unchecked type warning is unfortunately very difficult to avoid, so you will need the annotation anyways :/

